description: van gogh is a post impressionist painter, a Protestant clergyman family born in the rural area. He worked as a clerk and a business agent in his early years, and also served as a missioner in the mining area.He is full of fantasy and love to go to extremes. He suffers setbacks and failures in life.Finally, he devotes himself to painting and is determined to 'fight with himself in painting'.
name: Van Gogh's painting
